<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .heading p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .heading {
            width: 90%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-self: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

            .heading h1 {
                font-size: 50px;
                color: #000;
                margin-bottom: 25px;
                position: relative;
            }

                .heading h1::after {
                    content: "";
                    position: absolute;
                    width: 100%;
                    height: 4px;
                    display: block;
                    margin: 0 auto;
                    background-color: #a08679;
                }

        * {
            margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .image-container {
            width: calc(30% - 20px);
            margin: 10px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: block;
            margin: auto;
            object-fit: cover; /* Ensure the image covers the entire container */
        }

        .content {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            opacity: 0;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .image-container:hover .content {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .content h1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .content h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #a08679;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="heading">
        <h1>My Work</h1>
        <p>
            At KhumaloCraft, we're dedicated to showcasing the finest handcrafted products from artisans worldwide.
            Our platform serves as a global e-commerce hub, connecting discerning shoppers with unique, artisanal creations ranging from handcrafted bags,
            pots, and baskets to other meticulously crafted items. With a commitment to quality, authenticity, and supporting traditional craftsmanship,
            KhumaloCraft offers a curated selection of artisanal treasures that blend cultural heritage with contemporary style.
        </p>
    </div>

    

    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="~/images/bag.webp">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Handcrafted Bags</h1>
                <p>KhumaloCraft's handcrafted bags are artisanal masterpieces, blending style with functionality.</p>
                <h3>R350</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="~/images/pots.webp">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Handcrafted Pots</h1>
                <p>KhumaloCraft's handcrafted pots are symbols of cultural heritage and artistic tradition.</p>
                <h3>R450</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="~/images/basket.jpg">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Handcrafted Basket</h1>
                <p>KhumaloCraft's handcrafted baskets are both beautiful and functional.</p>
                <h3>R550</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

